  "texts": [
    "Alongside CFA, convergent and discriminant validity analyses were conducted to evaluate construct validity comprehensively.",
    "Utilizing the Lawshe method, the content validity ratio was determined based on the evaluations of 10 experts.",
    "With an acceptable content validity ratio of 0.62 for each item, it was agreed to omit six items (Items 6, 15, 17, 18, 27, 29) falling below this threshold from the scale.",
    "Subsequently, the content validity ratios of the remaining items were computed and yielded an average of 0.852.",
    "Thus, a draft scale comprising 24 items was formulated."
  ],
